"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:06:06.000Z","msg":"天體<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea40fb032667e7436cbaeaffc5372cd8742a323d","tid":2134384,"uid":15654,"like":11,"dislike":17,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"988c054ec2fcc43148b719e554bc08e39c577730","tid":2134384,"uid":148017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:06:06.000Z","msg":"天體<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"天體（astronomical object，也稱為celestial object）是在可觀測宇宙中，經由科學確認其存在的物體、或是結構[1]。<br />\n<br />\n天體可能像恆星、行星、彗星等結合較緊密的星體或類星體，也可能是指一個複雜的，彼此關聯較鬆散的結構，如星團、星系，其中可能包括許多其他的星體，甚至有其他更小的結構。<br />\n<br />\n天體的例子包括行星系、星團、星雲及星系，而小行星、 衛星、行星、恆星等則算是星體或類星體。彗星若只考慮其以冰和灰塵組成的彗核，是一個類星體，但若考慮彗核及其彗髮，則是一個關聯較鬆散的天體。<br />\n<br />\n貼返條link先 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A9%E9%AB%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%25AB%2594&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=855bfcb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A9%E9%AB%94</a>"},{"pid":"367d70fb65ffd886f0fd0f4167ca5f1c37246e3a","tid":2134384,"uid":200135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e56b4e4b9c305916bdeb65e773b4b74ea3caca74","tid":2134384,"uid":105140,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T16:59:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/j7CDb610Bg0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fj7CDb610Bg0&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=a222a1a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/j7CDb610Bg0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:12:31.000Z","msg":"識嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede201f1f4f85a3a14d9c2b9a8be51e76b64b73b","tid":2134384,"uid":57898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:19:24.000Z","msg":"私怨咪上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cl