"replyTime":"2020-07-31T18:24:17.000Z","msg":"有咩特別原因要推post<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"87c668c3b7e5dca8cde652d4213db4add5a777e4","tid":2134384,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea40fb032667e7436cbaeaffc5372cd8742a323d","tid":2134384,"uid":15654,"like":11,"dislike":17,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"988c054ec2fcc43148b719e554bc08e39c577730","tid":2134384,"uid":148017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:06:06.000Z","msg":"天體<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"天體（astronomical object，也稱為celestial object）是在可觀測宇宙中，經由科學確認其存在的物體、或是結構[1]。<br />\n<br />\n天體可能像恆星、行星、彗星等結合較緊密的星體或類星體，也可能是指一個複雜的，彼此關聯較鬆散的結構，如星團、星系，其中可能包括許多其他的星體，甚至有其他更小的結構。<br />\n<br />\n天體的例子包括行星系、星團、星雲及星系，而小行星、 衛星、行星、恆星等則算是星體或類星體。彗星若只考慮其以冰和灰塵組成的彗核，是一個類星體，但若考慮彗核及其彗髮，則是一個關聯較鬆散的天體。<br />\n<br />\n貼返條link先 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A9%E9%AB%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%25AB%2594&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=855bfcb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A9%E9%AB%94</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T18:30:03.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac91d3cdd49cad61743bbe735bdd49456f6191db","tid":2134384,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T19:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fffb2bfad70b43d5b4b2c9fbecf3c04bb111f4","tid":2134384,"uid":145927,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"8f0b9e522fe3e4d6709029cf7ed5adc2695f1516","tid":2134384,"uid":252142,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T19:23:25.000Z","msg"